high_descs: Head forward and to the left, to the sink.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Bring the potato to the fridge on the right.
Chill the potato in the fridge.
Bring the chilled potato to the black table on the left.
Put the chilled potato on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato on the small black table.

high_descs: Turn left and take a few step until you're even with the sink on you're right and then turn right and walk to the sink.
Get the potato that's in the sink.
Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk until you're even with the fridge on you're left then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Cool the potato off in the fridge before retrieving it and closing the door.
Take a step back then turn left and walk to the table then turn right and walk to the black stand.
Put the potato under the other potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold table on a black stand.

high_descs: Go to the sink in front of you and to the left.
Go to the fridge on your right.
Chill the apple in the fridge and take it out again.
Go to the black table on your left, at the end of the counter.
Put the apple on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple on the black table.
